The default SSID format seems to be '''AP'''XXXXXX, where '''XXXXXX''' is the last 6 hex digits of some portion of the MAC address. :Per '''SOHOware''''s manual, the AP password is unique to each device.
'''Askey''' may have manufactured this device.
==Additional external links== *[http://www.crn.com/news/networking/22101545/airgos-smart-antenna-technology-gets-heard-loud-and-clear.htm Initial retail price seems to have been $500]
